## RemoteConfig.fetchTimeMillis property

The Unix timestamp in milliseconds of the last <i>successful</i> fetch, or negative one if the [RemoteConfig](./remote-config.remoteconfig.md) instance either hasn't fetched or initialization is incomplete.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
fetchTimeMillis: number;
```
